snippet.title: Sam Houston
snippet.description:
#IStandWithDon and #IStandWithVic
Info:
Welcome to my channel. Politics, gaming, movies, pop culture and more are discussed on my channel. I use no scripts and make videos on the fly, so I will occasionally say stupid stuff. Production values are not very  high, I'm afraid. FYI am kinda a douchebag and curse a lot, so I apologize for (some) of my behavior I exhibit in my numerous vids. Along with glorious EFAP memes, Rhino Milk, and a ride from the Don, the Toxic Brood rides forward.
Stay 🅱ased


Don't forget to drink plenty of Rhino Milk while away from home, Praise the Don, Father of Tonald.
